This Risk Register was devolped as a part of the Online Booking System project to identify, assess, and manage potential risks that could impact project success.
The Register includes risk description, probability, impact, mitigation strategy, and ownership
# Risk Register â€“ Online Booking System Project

| ID | Risk Description | Probability | Impact | Priority | Mitigation Strategy | Owner | Status |
|----|------------------|-------------|--------|----------|---------------------|-------|--------|
| R1 | Delay in software development | Medium | High | High | Weekly progress tracking and milestone reviews | Project Coordinator | Open |
| R2 | Budget overrun | Low | High | Medium | Monitor budget and approve changes before execution | Project Manager | Open |
| R3 | Miscommunication between stakeholders | Medium | Medium | Medium | Regular status meetings and communication plan | Project Coordinator | Open |
| R4 | Technical implementation issues | Low | High | Medium | Technical testing and validation before release | Technical Team | Open |
| R5 | Resource availability issues | Medium | Medium | Medium | Confirm resource allocation in advance | Project Coordinator | Open |

## Risk Scoring Criteria

Probability Levels:
Low = unlikely to occur  
Medium = possible occurrence  
High = likely to occur  

Impact Levels:
Low = minor impact on project  
Medium = moderate impact  
High = major impact affecting timeline or delivery

